asparagus NEWS -- history of user-visible changes. 2014-11-26
Copyright (C) 2014 - 2015 Andreas Grapentin
See the end for copying conditions

Please send asparagus bug reports via
<http://github.com/oaken-source/asparagus/issues/>.

Version 0.6

* improved autotools integration

* added `given the c code` step
* added `when I compile` steps

* several bugfixes


----------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.5

* first release version

* added support for custom user-defined steps without the need to modify the
  dispatcher functions


